title: No. 9 Tech drops Sunday matinee to Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 9 Tech drops Sunday matinee to Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: WACO, Texas – No. 9 Texas Tech dropped its series finale versus Baylor, 11-7, on Sunday afternoon at Baylor Ballpark. The Red Raiders outscored the home team 5-0 from the fifth inning forward but it was not enough to overcome the nine-run margin the Bears built in the early innings.
